welcome_message_body: "Welcome to El Tabo, Chile! This charming city, known for its beautiful beaches and rich cultural heritage, invites you to explore and immerse yourself in its unique beauty. Enjoy your stay and discover all that El Tabo has to offer."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Valparaiso Airport handles all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Valparaiso Airport handles all air freight and cargo operations.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the free WiFi network throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal 1

terminals.name: Terminal 2

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
